Package: baseballscouting
Title: Baseball Scouting Report Generation
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Braeden", "Falzarano","bfalzarano@wesleyan.edu", role=c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Ernie", "Little","elittle@wesleyan.edu", role="aut"))
Description: The baseballscouting package allows users to analyze where pitchers and hitchers struggle and where they excel. Beyond this, users can run a simulation to see how the pitcher and batter would fare if they were to face off in a real game. 
